" Purpose:	Vim syntax file
" Language:	Bash - Unix Shell
" Maintainer:	Donovan Rebbechi elflord@pegasus.rutgers.edu
" URL:		http://pegasus.rutgers.edu/~elflord/vim/syntax/bash.vim
